	(text "DSP_IRQ <-\nDSP_IRQ ->\nDSP_RESET ->\n\npullups on irq.\n\nDSP Reset Circuit:\nUART DTRB \n 10kΩ Pull-up to VCC.\nUART DTRB \n 74LVC1G14 (Schmitt NOT Gate) Input.\nNOT Gate Output \n DSP /RESET.\nResult: Permanent Reset at power-on. Drive DTRB Low in BIOS to start DSP.\n"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 101.346 332.74 0)
